"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ebccf0e993ffb94d82c47fffad7a9fe45fdb673","tid":1470314,"uid":148987,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"打緊仗<br />\n捉到敵方做間諜係應該即啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔死都要重傷，震攝敵軍"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:02:26.000Z","msg":"甩p狗，請大家善用起底"},{"pid":"1d8889b8ff93b88fb9717cc99bc0d3eefcfe255e","tid":1470314,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<br />\n做錯事不道歉，是違反道德的啊。這個當然，但我們不是在小學課室，由班長和班主任裁判，我們是在戰場上，警察、法官、電視台、報紙、觀眾都是中共的人。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你道歉，對方就有材料展開政治謠言宣傳，而且要求你再為其他你無做過的事道歉（例如毆打北京記者），之後你拒絕，他們就向你開火射擊。</span></span>做錯了事就馬上走，不是道歉！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">普選勝利了，在民選元首認為安全的情況</span></span>，才為以往的錯失道歉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">道歉也是元首來做，不是民眾來做</span></span>，賠償也是用政府的錢，不是民間眾籌。"},{"pid":"c36cc66f8fe98771f1a11d78665a2911aa849ea4","tid":1470314,"uid":33786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ccd40c0c280b1be226f20dd1a1eaea78e9297cbc","tid":1470314,"uid":55775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"依家的確係有風向叫人唔好打狗同組人鏈保護 我地一定要正視 後果可以好危險"},{"pid":"47a412939d93fdb49b9b6990b1c75a7dfe3483b4","tid":1470314,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f25d495af6a299e4f8822dc26143a6031dc8e4","tid":1470314,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b9039b35c84ab7